  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to dmidecode</title>

    <para>
      <application>dmidecode</application> is a tool for dumping a computer's hardware information as described in its BIOS or UEFI firmware, including details about the system's processor, memory, and other components.
    </para>

